":"鸫","body":"嗯，我记得当时濑田学姐和千圣同学要进行舞台表演，\n来了非常多的观众。\n大家气势惊人，都想抢个好位置……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event238-04-059","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"虽然当时我没能做好，\n但或许是在拼命努力之后吧，\n我终于能『想方设法地』完成第一次遇到的事了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event238-04-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"『想方设法地』完成第一次遇到的事……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event238-04-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"嗯。这次或许也可以在『想方设法』的过程中，\n将事情变成『能够完成』的状态吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event238-04-062","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"（对啊……有道理。\n鸫学姐也不是一开始就什么都会的。\n她也有过很多烦恼，付出了很多努力……）","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"serious01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event238-04-063","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"啊啊，已经到必须离开学校的时间了！？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":32,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":32,"voiceId":"event238-04-064","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"好，打扫卫生和整理整顿就留到下次吧！\n得赶快准备一下，离开学校……咦？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event238-04-065","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"鸫","body":"这根绳子是什么？\n缠在手臂上，取不下来……嘿","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf_left01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event238-04-066","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":32}],"windowDisplayName":"LOCK","body":"鸫学姐，不行啊，这是……！！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"mo